{"tid":1935378,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有女權，但沒有母權","createTime":"2020-03-20T13:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T15:49:31.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dab5536a00c10835e95f3f898c548d476c458328","tid":1935378,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"或者大家仲未諗住做父母，<br />\n但拍拖戀愛，結婚，性慾，係同我們人類的繁殖慾掛勾。<br />\n<br />\n所謂母權，我指係產假，生孩子的福利或津貼等。香港基本欠奉。再加上高地價及高樓價政策，基本係對新家庭趕盡殺絕。<br />\n<br />\n在香港，有女權，女人可以同男人同等地位，但又沒有母權，女人基本上就唔會想生仔，自自然然也唔想結婚，拍拖戀愛的性趣也減少。<br />\n<br />\n所以香港女多男少，但毒撚搵女仍十分難。<br />\n<br />\n呢個問題，嚴格來說，唔係港女做成，而係政府做成。"},{"pid":"9d5d5e261accbf5f9cd8a97202b86d47a3015c7f","tid":1935378,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:48:12.000Z","msg":"港女表面對男人要求好高，實際來自政府對家庭的打壓。"},{"pid":"afc8e92a7fa6a9c81e80e3951b37b024e1120a0e","tid":1935378,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efbb367d912927751d3b922cb58375a7c9931d0f","tid":1935378,"uid":67814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"母權主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d952bc738fb4478fbe8f012f0b019af2bd8cb7e1","tid":1935378,"uid":135160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43aa6d15550364b415a5816e24965b8c13591335","tid":1935378,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T08:50:27.000Z","msg":"女多男少係總人口<br />\n後生係男多過女少少"},{"pid":"e26eede2fdfc0f21b636f04e7bf33669299ed459","tid":1935378,"uid":53510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T08:51:0